method.description:
Configures the reports to be generated by this task.

The contained reports can be configured by name and closures. Example:

<pre>
checkstyleTask {
  reports {
    html {
      destination "build/codenarc.html"
    }
  }
}
</pre>

<br><b class='param'>param:</b>closure The configuration
<br><br><b class='return'>returns:</b>The reports container

